1. Install the Ollama runtime
https://ollama.com/download

# After installation, you should be able to run the command below in your terminal (not Python)
> ollama run llama3

2. Keep the Ollama server running
Once itâ€™s installed, you can run it manually:
> ollama serve

# (Optional) Check if Ollama is already running
To confirm on Windows:
> netstat -ano | findstr 11434
